Subject: [PATCH v2 8/9] wifi: ath12k: Use RMW accessors for changing LNKCTL
Date: Wed, 17 May 2023 13:52:34 +0300
Message-Id: <20230517105235.29176-9-ilpo.jarvinen@linux.intel.com>
